oupVersion` | Combined GroupVersion for scheme registration |\n398: \n399: ### Auth Modes\n400: \n401: ```go\n402: type AuthMode string\n403: \n404: const (\n405:     AuthModePicod AuthMode = \"picod\"  // picod authentication\n406:     AuthModeNone  AuthMode = \"none\"   // No authentication\n407: )\n408: ```\n409: \n410: | Constant | Value | Description |\n411: |----------|-------|-------------|\n412: | `AuthModePicod` | `\"picod\"` | Use picod for session authentication |\n413: | `AuthModeNone` | `\"none\"` | No authentication required |\n414: \n415: ## Shared Types\n416: \n417: ### TargetPort\n418: \n419: Defines port configuration for runtime services.\n\n(Showing lines 360-419 of 577. Use offset=420 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"\n---\n\n# AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量\n\n## Overview\n\nAR-003 focuses on the shared types and constants used across AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRDs in the `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` module. These shared definitions ensure consistency and reduce duplication across the API.\n\n## Module Structure\n\n```\npkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n├── doc.go                    # Package documentation + kubebuilder markers\n├── register.go               # GroupVersion constants and scheme registration\n├── types.go                  # CRD type definitions (AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter, shared types)\n├── types_test.go             # Unit tests\n└── zz_generated.deepcopy.go  # Auto-generated deepcopy methods\n```\n","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/design.md","time":{"start":1775841185239,"end":1775841185254}}}}
