{"type":"text","timestamp":1775841251128,"sessionID":"ses_2879e3b29ffeWIj34sr2q2xrqJ","part":{"id":"prt_d7862fbfd00192Qn22PjamsYnU","messageID":"msg_d7862e49f001pykGqRKZtihrxR","sessionID":"ses_2879e3b29ffeWIj34sr2q2xrqJ","type":"text","text":"## Summary: AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量\n\n### Completed:\n\n**Constants** (`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go`):\n- `GroupName = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"`\n- `Version = \"v1alpha1\"`\n- `SchemeGroupVersion` \n- `Resource()` and `AddKnownTypes()` helpers\n\n**Shared Types** (`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`):\n- `TargetPort` - with kubebuilder validation (port 1-65535, protocol HTTP/HTTPS)\n- `PodTemplateSpec`\n- `PodSpec` - selective corev1.PodSpec subset\n- `ContainerSpec` - selective corev1.Container subset\n- `ContainerTemplateSpec`\n- `AuthMode` type with `AuthModePicod` and `AuthModeNone` constants\n\n**Validation & Tests**:\n- All kubebuilder validation markers added\n- DeepCopy methods generated (`zz_generated.deepcopy.go`)\n- All 15 unit tests passing\n- `go build ./pkg/apis/...` passes\n- `go vet ./pkg/apis/...` passes\n\n### Deferred:\nNone - all acceptance criteria from proposal.md have been implemented and verified.","time":{"start":1775841251126,"end":1775841251126}}}
